messages: 02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:35): Hey, my guy friend calls me bunny button. (:
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:36): You know what's funny...my mom got into an accident today.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:36): On the other hand I finally told this guy to man up and ask my friend out since she just broke up with this asshole.
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:39): Ambivolence is where you feel two conflicting emotions at the same time.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:40): Well, I'm not sad about my mother, just the fact that my father still thinks I should learn to drive.
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:40): but I don't know you, so I have no say in the matter.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:42): Thank God our generation isn't going down the shit.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:44): And I would have disconnected a long time ago if you were.
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:45): plenty of women are highly intelligent.
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:45): more so than me, that's for sure.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:46): Shit, do I really sound like a bloke?
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:47): I was all too aware of that only AFTER I'd asked if you were male. I'm sorry. And no, you don't.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:47): There is no need to apologize. That shows weakness.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:50): I don't think girls enjoy men calling out random body parts during moments of ectasy.
6abef31ebeef674838e51eb55ce0f43e (00:51): probably not, I'll avoid that in the future.
02f6fcd60c4417d8a5df54806d210e41 (00:55): Can I add you on msn?
